In this live recording from November 1962, Maria Callas sings the passionate soprano aria "Tu che le vanità" from Verdi's opera Don Carlo, with Georges Prêtre and the Orchestra and Chorus of the Royal Opera House, Covent Garden.

Recorded live at the Royal Opera House, Covent Garden, London 4.XI.1962.
Originally recorded and broadcast live at ATV as Golden Hour programmes.

